Body: Description: Hi team, After update GA 5.9.4.1 yesterday, we are not able to SSO login to NEP portal this morning, there was a looping at login.microsoft.com/login.srf (we integrated with Azure) Please note that after updated yesterday, we were still SSO login to the portal, the issue just happened since this morning Request to have a remote session to re producing the issue and fix it as soon as possible Thank you
